    {
      "key": "0577d80",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Ci sono così tanti PONTI in questa città.",
      "sourceEnText": "So many BRIDGES in this city.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_0577d80.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "KID_M",
      "durationMs": 2183,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:37:15Z",
      "textHash": "7980882d594e2717135dd18855f0bcdd94ee633916cbb4221fe6f8e02947d429"
    },
    {
      "key": "07ff8c5",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Adoro i pierogi!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love Pierogi!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_07ff8c5.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "KID_M",
      "durationMs": 1161,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:37:19Z",
      "textHash": "ee0112d557546afc3df5b623c0c770ae28890047e5068f0b328269e485802a87"
    },
    {
      "key": "089ea37",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Breslavia è davvero bellissima.",
      "sourceEnText": "Wroclaw is really beautiful.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_089ea37.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "KID_M",
      "durationMs": 1718,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:37:17Z",
      "textHash": "1839961a9d0c0b859e81210d57e5b9495fae56cbd01293ce9238681212989138"
    },
    {
      "key": "0bfcb05",
      "nodeTitle": "protagonist",
      "sourceText": "Se non riesci a trovarli, usa la mappa!",
      "sourceEnText": "If you can't find them, use the map!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_0bfcb05.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "SENIOR_M",
      "durationMs": 2183,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:35:26Z",
      "textHash": "b153e32441c7380051c7872d6f39de94c5b0f8cfd5ea8e814f9e524bcd063c16"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f36b7f",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_kayak",
      "sourceText": "Voglio guidare un piccolo KAYAK.",
      "sourceEnText": "I want to ride a small KAYAK.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_0f36b7f.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "KID_M",
      "durationMs": 1765,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:37:04Z",
      "textHash": "5691b07542b91c6e85a9f5a751a9a74b7b5986f685b0e6ed6724cd2877067533"
    },
    {
      "key": "barge_1",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_boat_barge",
      "sourceText": "Per secoli le chiatte (Barki) hanno trasportato carbone e sabbia sull'Odra.",
      "sourceEnText": "Barges (Barki) have carried coal and sand on the Odra for centuries.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_barge_1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4180,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:45Z",
      "textHash": "ac1066269be3c0b7297296ac02180d57cc26d9d2f653315de015fa1727f54914"
    },
    {
      "key": "barge_2",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_boat_barge",
      "sourceText": "Una chiatta è molto piatta. Perché?",
      "sourceEnText": "A barge is very flat. Why?",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_barge_2.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2043,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:47Z",
      "textHash": "e7f50e8dca52335b231eca33d601c150e133fee4e9d02ee4a2d6a5d898feab18"
    },
    {
      "key": "barge_3",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_boat_barge",
      "sourceText": "Per trasportare oggetti pesanti anche quando l'acqua non è profonda.",
      "sourceEnText": "To carry heavy things even when the water is not deep.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_barge_3.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3390,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:49Z",
      "textHash": "d4e932e5751330d4900eaab186ea2d128471fa16375f0c737ee9f5c3290dc394"
    },
    {
      "key": "barge_4",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_boat_barge",
      "sourceText": "Esatto! È un camion che galleggia.",
      "sourceEnText": "Exactly! It's a truck that floats.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_barge_4.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2229,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:51Z",
      "textHash": "f12b6861e60e012e5f3f06d70f79bac517c9940abdcbd028345c9f5dd914641c"
    },
    {
      "key": "barge_5",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_boat_barge",
      "sourceText": "Così può nascondersi dai nani",
      "sourceEnText": "So it can hide from dwarves",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_barge_5.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1533,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:54Z",
      "textHash": "cb1bbd2338b78efebba5b368694bab9d38e3d8e1a6e8e8da41ed56ca4b50ac50"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_house1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_boat_house",
      "sourceText": "Riparate le finestre della casa galleggiante!",
      "sourceEnText": "Fix the windows on the floating house!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_house1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2229,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:27Z",
      "textHash": "5d2f1db82e3abda396163525aeb5bae5832b2d9d1ce696ace761188eaaf24afb"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_house2",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_boat_house",
      "sourceText": "Una casa accogliente sull'Odra! Foto raccolta.",
      "sourceEnText": "A cozy home on the Odra! Photo collected.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_house2.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2694,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:29Z",
      "textHash": "d8d97d381472b37163ca4a3351e8894e2e273b3fd655370fe7a52b774cdb9b9f"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_map1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_odra_map",
      "sourceText": "Dimostra di sapere dove scorre il fiume!",
      "sourceEnText": "Prove you know where the river flows!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_map1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2090,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:34:05Z",
      "textHash": "e8d02e2f18c8b51d83a832d82921cba465c8b7c3181567028924857db767d77f"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_map2",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_odra_map",
      "sourceText": "La mappa è tornata! Mostra l'Oder che sfocia nel Mar Baltico.",
      "sourceEnText": "The map is back! It shows the Odra flowing into the Baltic Sea.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_map2.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3529,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:34:03Z",
      "textHash": "cfb2795ea205eb7107c4544a35532d1f5d9d8132b157c971a59a8221b6a7deca"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_redz1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_redzinski_bridge",
      "sourceText": "Ricostruiamo il pilone più alto di Breslavia!",
      "sourceEnText": "Rebuild the tallest pylon in Wrocław!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_redz1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2322,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:35:58Z",
      "textHash": "e975d2e206af12861f0114029dee2e8bc4f4f8b4214a9d0747dbdb41076001c7"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_sign1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_river_sign",
      "sourceText": "Antura ha coperto il cartello di fango! Puliscilo per vedere le onde.",
      "sourceEnText": "Antura covered the sign in mud! Wipe it clean to see the waves.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_sign1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3669,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:34:25Z",
      "textHash": "878070aede09a2abbc72abca4970bd10657b9760d3993aaa3f29fdb0f32199e4"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_sign2",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_river_sign",
      "sourceText": "Ottimo lavoro! Ora saprai sempre quando stai attraversando un fiume in Europa.",
      "sourceEnText": "Great job! Now you'll always know when you're crossing a river in Europe.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_sign2.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4365,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:34:21Z",
      "textHash": "ebb22d74604691143e21baf534a107393f75b427413294e4b2f2281e7ee42550"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_tour1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_boat_people",
      "sourceText": "Trova i turisti nascosti sul ponte!",
      "sourceEnText": "Find the tourists hidden on the deck!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_tour1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1858,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:43Z",
      "textHash": "975f0428dfbbd6fc7b58b40d6890f1390c7dd40fa9bc6c03d758ac44ebd4090c"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_train1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_bridge_train",
      "sourceText": "Abbina le scatole pesanti ai binari del treno!",
      "sourceEnText": "Match the heavy boxes to the train tracks!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_train1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2322,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:36:13Z",
      "textHash": "01b05ab09656e975b39d80eb9908273dcf976e8af2aac77293578eb25513cc49"
    },
    {
      "key": "ch_tum1",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_tumski_bridge",
      "sourceText": "Pulisci la ruggine da questo vecchio ponte di ferro!",
      "sourceEnText": "Clean the rust off this old iron bridge!",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_ch_tum1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2786,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:33:45Z",
      "textHash": "3f1c482b50fc7cfe830fbdc80c0d78404a66f4c8a02a2d3794bee86961112f77"
    },
    {
      "key": "chest_empty",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_river_sign",
      "sourceText": "Il baule è vuoto.",
      "sourceEnText": "The chest is empty.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_chest_empty.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
