      "nodeTitle": "quest_start",
      "sourceText": "Ci troviamo a Breslavia, la \"Città dei cento ponti\".",
      "sourceEnText": "We are in Wrocław, the \"City of a Hundred Bridges\".",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_start_1.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3204,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-03T20:35:51Z",
      "textHash": "c3ad42dac68c14d20cfadbf2cf9d7f638425bbe25316a7f3e155b6d342e88f72"
    },
    {
      "key": "start_2",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_start",
      "sourceText": "Oggi esploreremo il fiume, i ponti e le barche.",
      "sourceEnText": "Today we will explore the river, bridges and boats.",
      "audioFile": "pl_03_start_2.ogg",
      "voiceProfile": "francesco",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3065,
