      "key": "tour_1",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_boat_people",
      "sourceText": "Le imbarcazioni turistiche portano i turisti a visitare lo zoo e la cattedrale.",
      "sourceEnText": "Tourist boats take people to see the Zoo and the Cathedral.",
